<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Niwonapo mti bora
 Kristo aliponifia
 Kwangu pato ni hasara
 Kiburi nakichukia.

[V2]
 Na nisijivune, Bwana
 Ila kwa mauti yako;
 Upuzi sitaki tena,
 Ni chini ya damu yako.

[V3]
 Tangu kichwa hata nyayo,
 Zamwagwa pendo na hamu,
 Ndako pweke hamu hiyo,
 Pendo zako zimetimia.

[V4]
 Vitu vyote vya dunia,
 Si sadaka ya kutosha;
 Pendo zako zinawia
 Nafsi, mali, na maisha.</lyrics>
<title>Niwonapo Mti Bora TZR84</title>
<hymn_number>84</hymn_number>
</song>